{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act32side", "eventName": "水晶箭行動", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CR-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "消防通道", "storyInfo": "彩排的消息傳遍了多索雷斯。米沃什找到ELA，希望ELA能說服社區將藝術節改期，但無論社區還是雷內爾都有必須把時間定在那一天的充足理由。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G02", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨夜，一對巨大的木偶出現在本市街頭藝術社區中，其精美絕倫的程度足以讓每個見到它們的人瞠目結舌。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "社區中的藝術家設計製作了這對木偶，在昨天的彩排表演中，它們在月光下翩翩起舞。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可以看到拍攝的畫面中，在社區居民的精細操控下，它們舞姿靈動曼妙，好像真人一般。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眾所周知，該社區生活著大量的幫派分子與流浪漢，犯罪率居高不下，從沒有人敢靠近。但昨晚的表演吸引了許多人冒險去觀看。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來讓我們把畫面給到本台記者，看看現場觀眾是怎麼說的。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆，來份冰淇淋。", "name": "旅客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "攤販"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆？", "name": "旅客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_bar_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，請問這兩個木偶出現的時候你正在做什麼？", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我正在跑步，突然看到兩棟樓之間出現了一個巨大的人臉，嚇得我直接坐到地上。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來我壯著膽子，走上前去觀看了整場表演……", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看完後我的雙腿還在不停顫抖，不過這次不是被嚇到了，而是被震撼到了。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，先生，謝謝你願意接受我們的訪問。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，從這位先生走路的姿勢來看，他說的都是實話。現在讓我們把鏡頭對準那些生活在這裡的藝術家。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問問他們為何要造出如此巨大的一對木偶，又有怎樣的故事要向我們講述。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_020"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士們，先生們，終局請下注。", "name": "賭場荷官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_020"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓……", "name": "遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_020"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸位？", "name": "賭場荷官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_020"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g8_slums", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，看剛剛走過的女孩，她可是這裡的核心人物。小姑娘，請留步！", "name": "記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說你就是這場表演的總設計師，這麼小的年紀擔此大任……", "name": "記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了，要問什麼你快點問，我還有急事。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們想知道的事情非常簡單，為什麼那兩個木偶會出現在這裡？", "name": "記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如此大費周章，是為了將大家的目光吸引到這片社區嗎？", "name": "記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，幾年前我們有兩棟大樓在火災中焚毀，也沒見有幾個人把目光投向這裡啊。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火災……？", "name": "記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）果然沒什麼人記得。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的木偶表演就是為了紀念那場火災，紀念在那天離開我們的朋友。為此我們特意將開幕時間定在了火災發生的同一天。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但廣受關注的克里斯達爾藝術館開幕式也選在了當天進行，這會給你們帶來壓力嗎？", "name": "記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彩排前或許有，但現在基本上是沒有……", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#2$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……在藝術節正式開幕當天，表演效果只會更加轟動，我並不認為一個藝術展館的開幕典禮能和我們的表演平分秋色。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論以怎樣的噱頭粉飾，歸根究底，藝術館的開幕典禮向所有人傳達的不過只有一件事——", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就是雷內爾先生作為生意人的生意經。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_fastener", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼要關掉電視，米沃什？我正在看呢。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你該去睡一會覺了。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用啊，我現在一點也不睏。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#6$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去睡覺。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什……你為什麼板著臉，為什麼不替我高興？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#5$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去睡一覺吧，雷內爾。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十幾年過去了，那份本該屬於我的生日禮物終於回到了我的手上，我真的很開心。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？看你現在亂糟糟的模樣，你的話在我聽來沒有任何說服力。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那本來該是送給我的音樂盒……過生日前，她說要送我一個。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是老混蛋很不開心，她怎麼能創作一件不產生任何經濟效益的作品呢？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是天才，是明星，她的作品注定是要放在展會上被層層要價，怎麼能放在一個男孩的床頭櫃上寂寂無名呢？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但它回到你手中了，時隔多年，它最終還是物歸原主。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#5$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很喜歡，就算它被改得面目全非我也喜歡。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什，那她呢？她會喜歡我的回禮嗎？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你送給她的一切她都愛不釋手。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼不說話？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我確實想睡一會了，米沃什。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g9_gangsters", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到你在電視裡說那些話了，你不該在媒體面前這樣鋒芒畢露。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爹，你既然提議製造那個巨大的木偶，就不應該擔心我們的風頭是不是出得太過了。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，特克諾，我剛剛收到了一份信函，來自政府辦公室。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上面說，如果藝術節能夠成功舉辦，未來會有萊塔尼亞的文化交流代表團前來參觀我們的木偶表演。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的意思是，我們或許能得到政府的支持？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#4$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許更有可能被他們控制。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍閥、商人、政客，盯著這塊地皮的人只多不少。這些關注來得太快太突然，我有些壓力。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我的背不夠寬厚……", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爹，別這樣說，你還沒來這裡前，就算大火燒了一天一夜也無人問津，甚至連個報道的人都沒有。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾年正是因為有你在，大家才能安然無恙地生活，你的辛苦，我們所有人都看在眼裡。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為我們做了那麼多，不就是為了能讓大家走到陽光下舞蹈嗎？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們距離目標達成只有一步之遙，老爹你在擔心什麼啊？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#3$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我再想想……特克諾……", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#3$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能讓你們全無保護地走到陽光下。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#2$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g2_galleriessquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什先生，請問您和雷內爾先生有看到街頭藝術社區的木偶表演嗎？", "name": "記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們選擇在他們舉行藝術節的同一天舉辦克里斯達爾藝術館的開幕式，他們的成功彩排或許會分走很多本應屬於你們的關注。", "name": "記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這會讓你們感覺到壓力嗎？", "name": "記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "借過一下，小姐。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什先生，麻煩回答一下我們的問題！", "name": "記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很抱歉，今天我們並不打算回答任何問題。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什先生，請問保持沉默是否算是你們感受到壓力的表現？", "name": "記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_020"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請不要再靠近了，女士。", "name": "保全"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_020"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什先生！", "name": "記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_524_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g5_galleries", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA小姐到了嗎？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_020"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，她正在展廳內等候。", "name": "保全"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_020"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要和她談談，不要讓人靠近我們。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_020"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "保全"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_020"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g5_galleries", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA小姐，久等了，外面的記者簡直把這裡堵得水洩不通。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什先生，請問為什麼突然將我從社區召回？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和他們相處得很愉快，是嗎？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯，沒錯。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那裡生活的人，有非常旺盛的生命力。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們中的一些人，就算拖著病體，也依然能保持蓬勃的創作慾望。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然當下的世道“藝術家”稱號已經氾濫成災，但我必須承認，他們是些真正熱愛藝術的人。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那雷內爾呢？你又是怎麼看他的呢？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他……他是個有趣的人。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是如此嗎？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……很遺憾，在他身上，我看不到那些。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你曾跟我說，斯特凡先生的畫像讓你覺得不適。你沒見過他，他本人給人的不適感是畫像的一百倍。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是因為他，你本應在雷內爾眼裡看到那些的。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯特凡作為卡西米爾最知名的藝術品商人，會想盡一切辦法，從言語攻擊、暴力威脅到經濟控制……", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只為讓合作的藝術家按照自己的意願創作，其中甚至包括他的妻子，雷內爾的母親。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有創作者能夠忍受這些，她一定非常痛苦。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，夫人甚至親手毀掉了自己的作品來表達反抗，但一週後，那尊殘缺的雕像卻被飾以高深的哲學意義在拍賣場拍出天價。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她該離開。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#2$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不能，她不能把自己的孩子丟給那個自大的混蛋，尤其是一個很像自己的孩子。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你在這個時候讓我同情他，到底是為了什麼呢，米沃什先生？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是個敏銳的人，敏銳到近乎尖刻。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克里斯達爾藝術館的開幕式，定在了雷內爾母親離開的日子，那對他有著特殊的意義。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許你和你的小隊，能幫他一個小忙，不用很久，哪怕只是讓兩場活動錯開一天。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很抱歉，米沃什先生，請容我拒絕。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你們看到了新聞，就應該知道那一天對社區裡的人也有著特殊的意義。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#3$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA小姐……你應該試試的，剛剛的話並不是請求，而是提醒。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#6$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論他們的木偶表演多麼震撼人心，到了那天，都會在克里斯達爾藝術館的開幕式面前黯然失色。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#6$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你醒了？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛剛出去了一趟嗎？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我出去和ELA小姐見了一面。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她怎麼說？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她拒絕了。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "意料之中。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你還讓我把她叫過來。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是她來做的話，那場木偶表演還是能夠保全……或許未來某天，它會如那些人所願，成為這裡標誌性的演出。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但不會是在那天。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我簡直要憐憫他們了，為他們浪費在這場表演上的時間、心血、精力……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實話說，要不是有時間上的衝突，我甚至想親自去觀看他們的表演，比起樓底下那些被藝術投資商咀嚼過千次萬次的飯渣……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是那些傢伙的創作更令人感興趣。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾年很少聽到你說喜歡一件作品了。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，隨他們去吧。只是可惜……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論一件作品在初創時有多麼震撼人心，都無法與一場盛大的死亡相提並論。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後一批炸藥已經安設完畢，我明天會進行最後的調整，確保開幕式當天一切都會如願進行。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你為我做的一切，米沃什。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不客氣，你知道嗎，雷內爾，你剛剛談起毀滅時，眼睛裡閃爍著一些東西……", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很像，和你從前在我面前談起創作時眼睛裡流露出的東西很像。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是相似而已。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但對我來說，就已經足夠了。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#9$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#9$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephonering", "loop": "true", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……誰打來的？非得這個時候嗎？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，我去接吧。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#8$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為什麼一個電話接了這麼久？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#11$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（口型）對面一直在講個不停！", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（口型）到底是誰？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#11$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（口型）那個上尉！", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（口型）他打來幹嘛？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（口型）還能是為什麼？那片社區啊！", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#6$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，電話給我吧。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，馬特奧先生，你好，我現在正在忙，有什麼事之後再說。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephone"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人將電話乾脆利落地掛掉，然後狠狠扯斷了電話線。"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}